    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2019-04-10</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2019-07-08T18:44:37Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Jonny Wade Pediatric Cancer Research Act</b></p> <p>This bill terminates (1) the taxpayer election to designate $3 of income tax liability for financing of presidential election campaigns, (2) the Presidential Election Campaign Fund, and (3) the Presidential Primary Matching Payment Account.</p> <p>The Department of the Treasury must transfer the funds remaining in the Presidential Election Campaign Fund to the 10-Year Pediatric Research Initiative Fund. </p> <p>The National Institutes of Health (NIH) must prioritize certain pediatric research that does not replicate existing NIH research activities. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
